{"tid":981531,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"日復日 月復月","createTime":"2019-01-14T11:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T13:56:11.000Z","uid":207470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b04bb98d05c4db0c97f8a84b3f7136e076bf20ff","tid":981531,"uid":207470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:14:36.000Z","msg":"近來壓力好大<br />\n想搵份唔好話發揮所長<br />\n但至少有啲意思嘅工<br />\n<br />\n其實都搵到有啲工想做<br />\n自己想做表演或要走動嘅工<br />\n但好多都要 shift , <br />\n我又想工作以外學嘢，咁要定期上堂<br />\n<br />\n咁其實得翻 office 時間嘅工作選擇<br />\n問題，自己驚要坐 office 壓力會頂唔順<br />\n本身自己有啲情緒病， 一停低諗嘢就好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n其實都唔怕工種污糟 ，apply咗 迪迪士洗廁所但未有消息<br />\n目標今個星期 apply 海狗公園<br />\n但都驚未必請<br />\n<br />\n有無同路人可以指引吓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n取下暖都好<br />\n如果海狗唔請我我唔知仲有咩工岩我做。"},{"pid":"6a539893357cfa31131aba3ea4a69a6598a19eda","tid":981531,"uid":207470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:27:32.000Z","msg":"推一推，今日個頭好痛"},{"pid":"20e5d3c50df74e1d2d6286e63488d193698df6e3","tid":981531,"uid":207470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:04:59.000Z","msg":"。。"},{"pid":"3cd5487b93b7e464878a9d0c77543c9acf36a3db","tid":981531,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:09:05.000Z","msg":"你咁撚廢 做咩工都係咁架啦"},{"pid":"6650e5fa613a3b8b85248960c4d327c815b001bd","tid":981531,"uid":207470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cd5487b93b7e464878a9d0c77543c9acf36a3db","tid":981531,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:09:05.000Z","msg":"你咁撚廢 做咩工都係咁架啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:24:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82172137564af5642e08a04861bbc919bf324565","tid":981531,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6650e5fa613a3b8b85248960c4d327c815b001bd","tid":981531,"uid":207470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cd5487b93b